How old is Richard Jefferson?

Richard Jefferson is 45 years old.

Richard Jefferson was born in Los Angeles, California.

Richard Jefferson was born on June 21, 1980.

How tall is Richard Jefferson?

Richard Jefferson is 6-7 (201 cm) tall.

How much did Richard Jefferson weigh when playing?

Richard Jefferson weighed 233 lbs (105 kg) when playing.

Is Richard Jefferson in the Hall of Fame?

Richard Jefferson is not in the Hall of Fame.
